Maud Cressall https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maud_Cressall 0 Maud Cressall (1886–1962) was a British stage and film actress. Largely a theatre actress, she also appeared in nine silent films. She was at one point the protégé of W.S. Gilbert. Maud_Cressall ( 1886 – 1962 ) was a_British_stage_and_film_actress . Largely a_theatre_actress , she also appeared in nine_silent_films .
